---
title: "Your Portland-area window-cleaning specialists."
---
- content = data[:pages][:index]

%div.banner{ class: content[:banner][:class] }
  = stylesheet_link_tag "index"
  %div.container
    %div.logo-background.white-logo
      %h1= content[:banner][:heading]
      %h3= content[:banner][:subheading]
      %div.row
        %div.col-xs-offset-3.col-xs-6.col-sm-offset-4.col-sm-4
          %a.btn{ class: content[:banner][:button][:class] || "btn-default",
                href: content[:banner][:button][:url],
                role: "button" }= content[:banner][:button][:label]
    %hr
    %div.container.center-block
      %div.row.col-lg-12
        %div.col-lg-12.notice-text-box
          %h3 Leaky Gutters Need Us
          %hr
          %p#notice
            As beautiful as Autumn is, there is no denying it, it is
            %em
            %strong messy!
            Contact us today or try our online quote service and we will contact you. Also, find out more about how we clean your gutters on our Services Page.
